import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import { createProvider } from './vue-apollo'
import router from './router'
import 'jquery'
import 'popper.js'
import 'bootstrap'
import './assets/app.scss'
Vue.config.productionTip = false

new Vue({
    apolloProvider: createProvider(),
    router,
    render: h => h(App)
}).$mount('#app')
